{"tid":2296281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"小學生「知」字被圈錯    家長網上求教：究竟點寫至啱？","createTime":"2020-11-22T10:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T11:39:12.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"315de5c9023e98e2379d5728909a1966794dd0e2","tid":2296281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/v_j7Tc1WQ8qK9lozV7rauw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-11/3a167a40-2c8b-11eb-afd2-a823eb3d7d37\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fv_j7Tc1WQ8qK9lozV7rauw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-11%2F3a167a40-2c8b-11eb-afd2-a823eb3d7d37&h=6966ab2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟是嚴師出高徒，還是矯枉過正？近日有不少家長呻苦，指其子女練習寫中文字時，均被老師圈出錯誤。有家長早前在社交網站Facebook上載就讀小學兒子所寫的「知」字，其「矢」部被老師圈錯卻未有指正正確寫法，家長在網上查證亦未能找出錯誤原因，令他懊惱萬分：「真心誠意求教，究竟點寫至啱呢？」又自嘲：「生仔要先讀中文系」。<br />\n<br />\n該家長日前在Facebook群組「Tai Po大埔」上發文，貼上子女所寫的「知」字，苦嘆未能找出錯誤，嘲諷自己需要「重讀小學」。按圖片只見「矢」部寫得較大，「口」則較小。網民紛紛留言嘗試推測錯誤原因，有人指是兩邊字體大小不一，有人則指「矢」未有穿頭；較多人提出為「矢」字的第5劃不應是撇，而是一點。<br />\n<br />\n留言除了推測錯誤原因，亦有網民批評教師做法。網民Chun Kit So說：「呢啲咁嘅教育教到啲人變白癡」，另一網民Chloe Chan則說：「可以向老師講粗口？」但亦有網民為老師護航，Koen To說：「老師應該係真係想您小朋友學識寫一手好字」。"},{"pid":"305325645c256168a6189ae50fb8b0a28568ea95","tid":2296281,"uid":78243,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:54:21.000Z","msg":"最近咁多呢啲<br />\n小朋友唔鍾意讀書多得呢啲教畜唔少"},{"pid":"d2256e7ed13b503d1517417176c15a8e61171693","tid":2296281,"uid":282347,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:54:51.000Z","msg":"教畜咁「正确」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />由細開始扼殺小朋友嘅學習興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />害人不淺"},{"pid":"1cc55e0c63e1df65cdda4d2e9372a519b0dd715c","tid":2296281,"uid":126642,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:56:32.000Z","msg":"懶過閪，圈完唔俾返個佢個人覺得點寫先啱既寫法"},{"pid":"b039aa6af7163dfc3054fc273b56f4b432aaedcb","tid":2296281,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:57:25.000Z","msg":"支鬼teacher習慣打交义<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/udU1PtM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FudU1PtM.jpg&h=1ec7a355&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e898f99b93f5577975bd30da079d2cf2c7a84f45","tid":2296281,"uid":149041,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T10:57:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">有人則指「矢」未有穿頭     </span> <br />\n<br />\n講呢句嗰班...."},{"pid":"ac21064bd44fe2d220cd716a2cf8bd1288ee6488","tid":2296281,"uid":239270,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T11:00:28.000Z","msg":"較多人提出為「矢」字的第5劃不應是撇，而是一點<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊撚到點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d9ec7f390a2930c594c403faacb610d2102690","tid":2296281,"uid":1159,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T11:01:09.000Z","msg":"可能係個「矢」頭穿咗少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3de4bd26f986393b135744dc49ca5d1eed51eb4","tid":2296281,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T11:01:30.000Z","msg":"香港教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ad18c9e538e406a86ac286243f22d6c7f507fb","tid":2296281,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T11:02:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49da2d08d454d77c694059c5207520cfdd8468af","tid":2296281,"uid":6058,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ac21064bd44fe2d220cd716a2cf8bd1288ee6488","tid":2296281,"uid":239270,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score